    "description": "an ultra-efficient cloud-based pipeline for mapping allele-specific DNA methylation.\n\nLast updated: July 31, 2020. Please check our preprint on biorxiv and our published paper on Bioinformatics.\n\nMed Google Cloud Platform kan du oprette, implementere og skalere apps, websites og tjenester på den samme infrastruktur som Google.\n\nFortsæt til Google Cloud Platform.\n\nSkriv den tekst, du hører eller ser.\n\nTo be able use CloudASM, you need to create an account on https://cloud.google.com/ and set up how you want to be billed (e.g. with a credit card). As of January 2020, GCP offers $300 in credits for opening an account -- which is enough to test this pipeline.",
